{"tid":1853091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】內地媒體斷章取義病毒可傳貓狗 疑引民眾恐慌拋擲貓咪至死","createTime":"2020-01-30T18:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T00:45:10.000Z","uid":74637,"like":14,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7382ef40eacf8897f5bc24698b5eb3b8016ac5","tid":1853091,"uid":74637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:45:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200130/3O4QB27NRTAYAK5OTXBWFP4JYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200130%2F3O4QB27NRTAYAK5OTXBWFP4JYI%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=1cb1fbba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200130%2F3O4QB27NRTAYAK5OTXBWFP4JYI%2F&h=9dd39416\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200130/3O4QB27NRTAYAK5OTXBWFP4JYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAgtbCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAgtbCw.jpg&h=91875b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地面對疫情屢屢傳出不實消息，那邊廂傳出養貓可抗肺炎，導致武漢出現「搶貓潮」後，這邊廂又突然盛傳新型冠狀病毒可傳染給貓狗，疑似引起民眾恐慌並直接把家中貓咪從高空拋擲而下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日有中國專家指引發武漢肺炎的新型冠狀病毒有機會在哺乳類間傳播，而世界衛生組織已澄清未有證據顯示家寵如貓狗會感染武漢肺炎。但日前上海領養之家就在社交平台上表示，有媒體斷章取義指這種病毒可傳染給貓狗，引發多地出現貓狗棄養潮。網上便盛傳一張微信對話截圖，顯示疑似有內地飼主因為以上虛假消息，而把家中的貓咪連同寵物用品全部丟棄。<br />\n<br />\n該文章又引述消息指，甚至有民眾疑似因為恐慌而直接把家中貓咪從高空拋擲而下。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從轉發的照片中可見有數隻貓咪躺於地上，旁邊有疑為血跡的紅色液體。</span></strong>又有內地網民回覆該張照片表示，並非只有圖中所見的3隻，而是共有5隻。消息傳出後，不少網民怒批行為自私而殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n幾撚時死啊啲大陸佬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05557b909f2b5bdc6de62656b5bdb4ee7ebde642","tid":1853091,"uid":27946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:47:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77779250a24dc07648910ec9664ea020b7ecf500","tid":1853091,"uid":213607,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:48:14.000Z","msg":"raining cats and dogs"},{"pid":"43c11b8a1003ab1571456fa97685afa72aa383fa","tid":1853091,"uid":74637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:48:18.000Z","msg":"憑乜嘢咁樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次支爆真係抵撚死"},{"pid":"46bfd8864a2d28eef57e2fa815d8c830142057a0","tid":1853091,"uid":288255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:48:38.000Z","msg":"尋日爭住養貓，今日爭住殺貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2be27d3b520f97a21f70066500d1e677aa679c9","tid":1853091,"uid":52763,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:49:09.000Z","msg":"來生不做中國貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9ed14dcef04d4eb02bc84ad5534a1304ba6dc9","tid":1853091,"uid":52763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46bfd8864a2d28eef57e2fa815d8c830142057a0","tid":1853091,"uid":288255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:48:38.000Z","msg":"尋日爭住養貓，今日爭住殺貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"可能比人fake左即刻掉落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e778305dbbd78ad2fa220a06e46484a818bc3728","tid":1853091,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:53:56.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=